column1: #Summary1=(human1) In this video, Christine Lee studies for and takes for her college final exams in neuroscience and chemistry, and then surprises her friend Megumi with donuts for her birthday.

#Summary2=(claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022) A student shares updates about studying for their neuroscience final exam, including late-night study sessions and anxiety before the test, then celebrates their friend Megumi's 20th birthday by surprising her with donuts and tulips after finishing the exam.

#Summary3=(gpt4o) A college student details a hectic week leading up to their neuroscience final exam, navigating between studying, meetings, and managing social media mishaps, culminating in a mixture of nervousness and relief on exam day, followed by a joyful surprise birthday celebration for a friend with donuts and friendly camaraderie captured on video.

#Summary4=(Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct) A college student, Kat, is preparing for her neuroscience final exam, studying and using the Pomodoro technique to manage her time, while also taking care of personal tasks like ordering donuts for her friend's birthday celebration.
